<p>direction, surprised though to find myself so weak when I endeavoured to get on the floor, would have fallen only for the timely assistance of my good Canadian Sister.</p>
<p>Thursday 4.10.17  - Friday 5.10.17<br/>Both days have been up for a while, gradually becoming stronger.  Received a fine bunch of mail from home 22-29 July.</p>
<p>Saturday 6.10.17<br/>Break in the weather.  September was a beautiful month as far as weather was concerned.  Convoy of "Huns" taken into hospital here.</p>
<p>Sunday 7.10.17 to Tuesday 9.10.17<br/>Found my legs again</p>
